<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Verification - NBKRIST Societies</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f8fafc;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background: #1e293b;
        color: white;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .header p {
        margin: 0;
        opacity: 0.8;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 32px 24px;
      }
      .greeting {
        color: #334155;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .greeting strong {
        color: #1e293b;
      }
      .otp-section {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 32px 0;
      }
      .otp-label {
        color: #64748b;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .otp-box {
        background: #f1f5f9;
        border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 16px auto;
        max-width: 200px;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1e293b;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      }
      .instructions {
        color: #475569;
        font-size: 14px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 16px;
      }
      .notice {
        background: #fef3c7;
        border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .notice p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #92400e;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f8fafc;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }
      .footer p {
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        color: #64748b;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      .footer .company {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #334155;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        body {
          padding: 10px;
        }
        .container {
          border-radius: 6px;
        }
        .header {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }
        .footer {
          padding: 20px 16px;
        }
        .otp-code {
          font-size: 28px;
          letter-spacing: 4px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>NBKRIST Societies</h1>
        <p>N.B.K.R. Institute of Science & Technology</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">Dear <strong><%= name %></strong>,</div>

        <p style="color: #334155; margin-bottom: 24px">
          Thank you for registering with NBKRIST Societies. To complete your
          email verification and secure your account, please use the
          verification code below:
        </p>

        <div class="otp-section">
          <div class="otp-label">Verification Code</div>
          <div class="otp-box">
            <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
          </div>
          <div class="instructions">
            This code will expire in <strong>10 minutes</strong>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="notice">
          <p>
            <strong>Security Reminder:</strong> Never share this verification
            code with anyone. Our team will never ask for this code via phone or
            email.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 24px">
          If you didn't request this verification, please disregard this email
          or contact our support team if you have concerns about your account
          security.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p class="company">NBKRIST Societies Platform</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
        <p>For support, contact us at support@nbkrist.edu</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
